	dprr:hasNoteText "Dig. 11.5.2.1. Author of a law limiting wagers to contests virtutis causa. The date is uncertain but precedes 81, if the Lex Cornelia on the same topic was carried by Sulla. No title preserved. See Niccolini, FTP 433." ;
